{"tid":2233741,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"法庭要求何君堯14日内提供林卓廷為主謀證據","createTime":"2020-10-07T10:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T15:13:27.000Z","uid":36155,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"05093dab6bee5930ddb12ff399f2efe6974135fd","tid":2233741,"uid":36155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:58:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/534865589914032/posts/3343783772355519/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F534865589914032%2Fposts%2F3343783772355519%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmVKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=49c5348b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/534865589914032/posts/3343783772355519/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷就721告何君堯誹謗案今日第一堂，何君堯由於未有回應涉嫌誹謗言論的事實根據等資料，最終法庭指令佢需於14日內回應我方眾多提問，包括有何事實根據指721當日林卓廷喺西環帶幾百人入元朗搞事，法庭同時命令何君堯負責今堂訟費。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯 (Junius Ho Kwan Yiu)<br />\n#記得答問題啦<br />\n#仲要俾訟費喎"},{"pid":"708b21ede2f23e85584bc43576a95faa17cd8d45","tid":2233741,"uid":36155,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:00:25.000Z","msg":"唔知大波華會唔會介入呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b93e85503f9b73d205ceb0f28217ca0d5ee5541","tid":2233741,"uid":36155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2164bd3bf009d79746a6a345f1210ad52478aca6","tid":2233741,"uid":36155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:09:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c873135f60c7031318f183c0422620549d90799","tid":2233741,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse